{"title":"大山的爱（三首）","authors":["李蔚红"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":5,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山的爱（三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李蔚红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩　子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是个孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤着脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀大山的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩上颤颤的水桶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头起伏的愿望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他还会吹牧羊曲呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树叶子轻轻地贴在唇上……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游人需要甜的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他担来甘泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山需要咸的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他洒下汗浆……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是大山的孩子啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他快乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把快乐在深山里牧放……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真想为他戴条红领巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可大山给他的更漂亮："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上的红叶和天上的霞光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇着枫叶的溪流里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她在洗衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清香的肥皂泡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从指缝探出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又去追赶游鱼……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日的灰暗洗尽了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日的艰涩洗尽了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把洁净与明丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晾上泛出新绿的草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许，她还不知道有了洗衣机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但听那支回旋的洗衣曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想说：她是时代的洗衣机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早　饭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是鸡叫醒的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是钟敲醒的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催她起得这么早"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻点上灶火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从锅里端出农家的早饭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活热了、熟了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗粗细细，喂育新的一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"递给丈夫白面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己咬起窝头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子大口大口吮着乳汁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦，是昨夜的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳走进窗棂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邀她一起下田……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}